place.name: FRESHWATER
place.gazetteerText: Freshwater, par. and vil., SW. coast Isle of Wight, on river Yar, 1½ mile SW. of Yarmouth -- par., 4836 ac. and 478 tidal water and foreshore, pop. 2809; P.O., T.O., 1 Bank; 1 mile S. of vil. is the vil. of F. Gate. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
